erequisite)\n84: - AR-022 — CLI publish command (follows build)\n\n(End of file - total 84 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-021 — CLI build 命令 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-021 — CLI build 命令 |\n| Module | `cmd/cli` |\n| Language | Python |\n| Size | M |\n| Stage | ST-0 |\n\n[TO BE FILLED: Describe the build command overview]\n\n---\n\n## Architecture\n\n### System Context\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-021/design.md","time":{"start":1775870084162,"end":1775870084175}}}}
