 Out of Scope\n\n[TO BE FILLED: Define out of scope items]\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-021/spec.md","time":{"start":1775870091590,"end":1775870091600}}}}
